item.title: About Me
item.description: Hiyo! I am currently a 20 year old, who is attending school at University at Buffalo. On top of my academics, I’m currently an intern at the leading cloud foundry consultancy company - Stark & Wayne. I am expected to graduate in 2020 with a B.S in Computer Science. I am just enjoying the ride and am using Hugo to create my website! Some of my hobbies include going hiking, climbing, going to the gym and when I have spare time, I play League of Legends in my spare time.
